Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:10.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hilarious! 30 year anniversary special.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is "Your First Errand".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.83,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(276.75,903)}George Tokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.83,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(788.625,903)}Moriguchi Hiroko
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.50,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(280.125,909)}Amami Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.50,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.125,783)\fs35}Football hour:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.50,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(766.125,847)}Gotou Terumoto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.87,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(527.625,903)}Hotta Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.87,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(187.875,903)}Fujimoto Miki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.87,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878.625,903)}Ichikawa Ebizou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Tokoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow "My First Errand"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,has been on the air for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it been 30 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning you've been doing this show since you were 6?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for math.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And to commemorate those 30 we've brought some wonderful guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow we got Mr. Ebizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.46,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(990,875)}Father of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What I know is that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he keeps writing about the program on his personal blog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The most famous fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I always watch the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikitty mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:01:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One more is on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(207,831)\fs50\c&HBB7AF2&}Pregnant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amazing silhouette.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you due?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm due at the end of this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost popping out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine for you to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so much free time while anticipating.{\alphaFF\t(859,859,\alpha0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Amami, what do you think of "Errand"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,884.2)}I always watch it and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Todays errands will also make you laugh and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The first errand is by a 4 year old boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:35.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,November last year a magnificent wedding was held in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:41.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the wedding of a kid who went on his first errand 21 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not going well since it's the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:51.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's laughing today but back then he cried hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Very traditional. \N - So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keiichirou is 25 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:01.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His first errand was also a first for his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:06.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An errand that became an irreplaceable family memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's show it to begin the 30 year anniversary special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:16.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(3955,0,\alphaFF)}21 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:19.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On the day of moving out of the company provided housing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:24.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keiichirou went on his first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,8 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:28.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are ready to move out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from the company housing where his parents married.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:35.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've lived here for 6 years and 3 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:40.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Giving birth to a son and a daughter and becoming a 4 unit family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:45.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To the 4 year old Keiichirou this home has been the center of his entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring it all to the new house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:52.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother decided on this errand on the day of moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:58.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wants to teach Keiichirou the importance of saying your goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:04.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His two friends from the block who have known each other since they were babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:10.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Parting with your dear friends for the first time is something his mother also has experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The moving truck has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Keichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already 10 so mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will make him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go on an errand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.22,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture that I took at the farewell party the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She took a picture that he was asked to print 2 copies from the photo store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:33.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the picture his father took at the farewell party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will hand it to Shougo and Yuuseke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:38.30,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(733.5,687)}Yuusuke
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:38.30,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(330.75,687)}Shougo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After that {\alphaFF\t(1291,1291,\alpha0)}go greet your doctor {\alphaFF\t(3927,2937,\alpha0)}Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pediatric doctor Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:47.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She helped take care of his asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's told to bring her flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Give it to Meichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:56.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The goat Meichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we didn't get to say bye the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.55,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Since we are moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.36,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:08.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a special treat on this day she's cut up fresh vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:12.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's got 3 people and a goat to say goodbye to. Better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei, if you are slow then the truck will depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That would be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}So I will give you this watch so you can keep track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papas watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:25.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How cool. Really makes you overcome anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He still can't tell the time but he understands his fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because the dial has an arrow that the hand can point to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:35.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keiichirou, be back by then. He's given a 1 hour limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's all in the same block.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shougo, Yuuseke, the preschool teacher Nakamura and the goat Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's an errand to say your goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The oath between two men - a father and his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.50,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1655,0,\alphaFF)}I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:59.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,3 minutes away is the photo store inside of the supermarket his mother always shops at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:06.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All of Keiichirous pictures since his birth have been handled by this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really moving away from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:13.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Those 4 years have added up to 10 complete photo albums.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's become so big already. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:21.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up he needs to pick up some flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:24.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cause he's supposed to bring them to his teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He picked the doctors favorite peach blossoms and strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,How smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's always being welcomed even on days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:34.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been taken really good care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:37.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's known her since he was 7 months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.52,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's in the middle of a medical examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,He just walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I came by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You will give this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:53.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Saginomiya in Nakano ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,Very specific info.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is able to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Be kind to your sister Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.61,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1723,0,\alphaff)}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,So dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:07.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keiichirou that night you caught pneumonia was cutting it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Your asthma will surely get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:15.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's checking the arrow on his fathers watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right. He has to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The truck is packed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's running again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has arrived at Shougos house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The three of them are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,He can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Are they not home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite having brought the photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite wanting to say goodbye, Shou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.15,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, they are inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Keichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shou has forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That Kei is leaving today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.59,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I didn't come to play. Here's a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.03,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2126,0,\alphaFF)\pos(540,940.2)}One of them is for Shou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:58.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A picture from the goodbye party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:01.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right... Kei is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:04.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As he realizes that Shou falls silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Aww~ he must be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:08.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They really love each other but Shou is too shy to express it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today he has to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:14.25,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will not always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bashful Shou won't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:21.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With wide eyes he's holding back faint tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The truck is waiting so he's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:30.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shou was acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:33.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite having brought him a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He didn't even say bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Time to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papas watch says...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:46.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's still fine. There are 30 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's properly paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There she is, Meichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:54.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meichan is the baby goat kept by the children's center.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been feeding her for 1 year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.26,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(177.75,73)}Scary, scary, scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They couldn't keep animals at the company housing but he was glad to have Meichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:13.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Broccoli stems. His mother has packed it with Meichan's favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he ever be able to feed her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Saginomiya is far from here, Meichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's suddenly becoming melancholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When you do I have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Suddenly he remembers his dads watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The time has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,The time passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's running all he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:59.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mom, dad and the truck is not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought we had left?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:09.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not like they can just leave Keiichirou behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go to Yuusuke's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1353,0,\alphaFF)\pos(153,927.4)}I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.64,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1486,0,\alphaFF)\pos(212.4,941.8)}I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:21.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He really believed that they had left him for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are able to go by yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go while I clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and see Yuusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with not seeing him again. He's probably waiting at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The fright from thinking he was abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:42.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He wasn't able to go Yuusuke's house so his regret made him suddenly dejected back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:47.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But his mother intends to make him go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.03,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(361.8,933.8)}I forgot to go to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.60,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242.1,930.6)}Yuuseke's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:54.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father also intends to make him go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be sad if you didn't go and just cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strong boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring it in again with Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:06.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father used to be in the rugby club in Keio University.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An oath between men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keiichirou is not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 4 unit family is one team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:15.66,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1621,0,\alphaFF)}I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father gave him his handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:24.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And told him to wipe his tears and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hoping to make Keiichirou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,properly say his goodbyes to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:35.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The entertaining park, the back streets he ran through
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and his beloved friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here's Yuusuke's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The stairs he climbed every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.46,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's Hara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.20,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He stopped crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His fathers handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The handkerchief to wipe away the tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(2555,0,\alphaFF)\pos(540,941.8)}Why are you crying that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2152,0,\alphaFF)}Why are {\i1}you{\i0} crying, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:38.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Previously when... came home #!&%...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:41.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was about to leave without saying good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke's prized possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:49.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's giving his Toy Story figures of Woody, Buzz and Rex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,Those are indeed prized items.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.66,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:56.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You don't have to give them. I already have lots of toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having made so many precious memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Heading towards a new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's tired for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:30.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cause he has filled his minds photo album with memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,He did his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Shou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Yuusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:39.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone, everyone, be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To fill his heart with goodbyes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:48.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,opens his eyes and makes him ready to face his next home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keiichirou what follows goodbye is hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:58.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A "hello errand" is waiting for you in a new town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:07.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\t(2588,0,\alphaFF)}21 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Saying hello again
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to Mami who he met at his company's initiation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:19.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He grew up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:23.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keiichirou is a new employee at a major food company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has just started his salaryman life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dad, he has risen from the ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And his relationship to his parents is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3826,0,\alphaFF)}It's still running smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's still running?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the watch from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't use it much but {\alphaFF\t(1394,1394,\alpha0)}I just can't throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534.375,991)}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To commemorate your first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is that what he has planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get a shot with you and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:14:04.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The watch matches him as he has taken after his beloved cool dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:11.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Japanese rugby captain Tanaka's son's first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:17.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I will carry it just like my beloved dad" but it ends up in a sticky situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:24.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So moving that it even exceeds his fathers' expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been wonderful right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was so moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Ebizou {\alphaFF\t(1592,1592,\alpha0)}you were also teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,485,\alpha0)}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This show really throws you off your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You get hit from all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid himself but also the people around him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and for the crying mother who clearly knows what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was just moved to see his emotional expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It really throws you off your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\alphaFF\t(556,556,\alpha0)}dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to avert my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And Amami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My nose immediately {\alphaFF\t(652,652,\alpha0)}started to drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unexpecedly early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuusuke was also a great kid. Wanting to give his prized possesion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that kids can refuse such an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids will say "I don't need it".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they understand what the toys mean to the other kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the poster girl at a sushi restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(525.375,101)\fs38}Kanbanmusume (literally: poster girl): A pretty girl who attracts customers to come inside a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(870.75,171)}Shizuoka ● Itou city
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:27.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the hot spring district of Itou, Izu Prefecture, where easygoing (Nonki) sushi can be found at Nonki sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:29.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a high-end sushi restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:31.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad is a second generation chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:35.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Close to the ocean and the mountains so the ingredients are abundant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:41.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mazuma wasabi from Amagi and the golden eye snapper from Shimoda which is a bit fatty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:48.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's on a road where few cars pass by so this is a stop that people go out of their way to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:51.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a family-run establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:57.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The proprietress is the grandmother and the great-grandmother is the great-proprietress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(211.5,860.2)\alphaFF\t(0,453,\alpha0)}Great-grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,453,\alpha0)\pos(815.4,521)}Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Little miss proprietress, please also do it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Little miss proprietress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make it sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:10.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Yuna. She's in work-mode when she wears an apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When we are here and you have an apron on what do you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today she is hosting at the masters' restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you the entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:28.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To put the young proprietress on her first errand the master has thought of a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The proprietress-to-be, her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? This is Nonki Sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:39.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taking an order over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The homepa spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:46.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Homepa spread for home parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Homepa?
