Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:31.46,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916.2,450.6)\alphaFF\t(0,487,\alpha0)}Big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:41.31,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,487,\alpha0)\pos(244.8,622.4)}Yuna
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:38.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Actually her brother recently had his errand debut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and she's been asking enthusiastically "When can I go?"
