Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:47.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She needs to get white radish sprouts, avocado and cucumber for the sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:51.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On top of that, spring onions and 20 plates.
