Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.45,0:24:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.32,0:24:33.68,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.68,0:24:36.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not Thai curry but radish sprouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.59,0:24:38.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And kamaboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.72,0:24:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamaboko?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.76,0:24:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.42,0:24:41.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamaboko, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.02,0:24:43.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Was it not kamaboko?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.76,0:24:45.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She senses that it's kinda wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:49.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:53.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,So it was kamaboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:55.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamaboko, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.01,0:24:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.71,0:25:02.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She put in two kamaboko pastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.38,0:25:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.71,0:25:05.82,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.82,0:25:07.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? And the paper plates?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.62,0:25:09.75,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.39,0:25:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.75,0:25:13.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seems like her head was full of radish sprouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:16.96,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.59,0:25:17.79,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a grand errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are back?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.39,0:25:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.73,0:25:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought the spring onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.80,0:25:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you purchase more?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.64,0:25:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it. {\alphaFF\t(1684,1684,\alpha0)}Radish sprouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.60,0:25:30.74,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I bought yet another radish sprout box.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.71,0:25:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah two. Proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.74,0:25:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.31,0:25:33.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I accidentally purchased kamaboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.64,0:25:35.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She did notice that it was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.08,0:25:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for kamaboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.15,0:25:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Steamed fish paste, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.48,0:25:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say steamed fish paste but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.65,0:25:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We could put it in the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.19,0:25:44.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You better do. Put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.39,0:25:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And avocado?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.59,0:25:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.73,0:25:49.89,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.33,0:25:54.16,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(1988,0,\alphaFF)}I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.07,0:25:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Yuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.67,0:25:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.44,0:25:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.27,0:26:00.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.54,0:26:01.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's going again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.30,0:26:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.87,0:26:02.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.11,0:26:05.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's not giving up, the little proprietress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.48,0:26:07.41,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Avocados.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.41,0:26:09.35,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Avocados.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:13.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The third time she repeats "avocados".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.62,0:26:14.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.06,0:26:21.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.03,0:26:26.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. Avocados.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.36,0:26:30.97,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Avocado.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.70,0:26:29.10,Studio,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.97,0:26:32.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.20,0:26:37.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She heads straight to the cashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.74,0:26:40.64,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,For grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.41,0:26:44.01,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I better get a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.01,0:26:46.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's doing unnecessary things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.22,0:26:48.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her grandmas favorite food is Mitarashi dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.85,0:26:50.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She went straight to the checkout.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.19,0:26:51.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,She went to the cashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.82,0:26:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. {\alphaFF\t(1324,1324,\alpha0)}Is dango all you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.93,0:26:59.26,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Avocados and {\alphaFF\t(2419,2419,\alpha0)}paper plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.43,0:27:00.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,How good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.26,0:27:01.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was able to say it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.37,0:27:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.30,0:27:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Store manager, {\alphaFF\t(521,521,\alpha0)}please come to {\alphaFF\t(1021,1021,\alpha0)}checkout Nr. 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.10,0:27:05.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,1001)}The store manager again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.84,0:27:09.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The store manager has been put in charge{\alphaFF\t(985,985,\alpha0)} of the small proprietress.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.71,0:27:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.31,0:27:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.15,0:27:18.92,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2819,0,\alphaFF)}Avocados and...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.38,0:27:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2819,0,\alphaFF)}Avocados and...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.02,0:27:23.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Avocados and you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.19,0:27:25.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,Please remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.19,0:27:27.02,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,paper plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.02,0:27:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Paper plates{\alphaFF\t(1693,1693,\alpha0)} and avocados.{\alphaFF\t(2828,2828,\alpha0)} Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.69,0:27:31.29,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(541.286,1007.797)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.29,0:27:33.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Apologies for keeping you busy, store manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.03,0:27:36.97,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Getting two.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.97,0:27:39.37,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I will pick this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:40.27,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.27,0:27:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.47,0:27:43.77,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Paper plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.01,0:27:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the paper plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.68,0:27:49.85,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:51.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.68,0:27:52.15,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.15,0:27:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.85,0:27:54.02,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.55,0:27:58.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has finally gotten all the items.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.85,0:27:59.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:28:00.42,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.76,0:28:03.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Third time paying today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.23,0:28:05.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Looking for the wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.96,0:28:08.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.77,0:28:11.54,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh, it was lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.54,0:28:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lose the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.44,0:28:14.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.87,0:28:17.51,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.14,0:28:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.24,0:28:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. There's no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.61,0:28:22.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.61,0:28:25.18,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,What should I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.85,0:28:26.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right. What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.18,0:28:26.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.42,0:28:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.42,0:28:32.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not okay to not pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.02,0:28:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really no money? What about behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.76,0:28:35.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a pat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.99,0:28:39.03,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.93,0:28:40.33,Studio,,0,0,0,,Pat down in a supermarket!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.10,0:28:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do without the items?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.23,0:28:45.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.07,0:28:48.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Around that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.61,0:28:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She forgot her purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.61,0:28:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.44,0:28:54.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She forgot it at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.21,0:28:56.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When she came back the second time...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.45,0:28:58.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,She left it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.78,0:29:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yuna, can you go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.65,0:29:04.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.05,0:29:07.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The culprit of the wallet mystery is the mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.65,0:29:05.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,The mother left it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.99,0:29:11.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The proprietress-to-be taking responsibility runs with all her might.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.36,0:29:13.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's how it's gotta be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.77,0:29:16.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,Back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.00,0:29:17.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.93,0:29:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yunachan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.70,0:29:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. {\alphaFF\t(2392,2392,\alpha0)}I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.11,0:29:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.34,0:29:27.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please do it better, proprietress-to-be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.54,0:29:29.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so mad. So mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.51,0:29:30.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this she can finally pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.88,0:29:34.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The little proprietress has purchased everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.82,0:29:37.62,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.95,0:29:41.32,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I bought it all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.42,0:29:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You did. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.32,0:29:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.66,0:29:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being a forgetful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.33,0:29:48.17,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.17,0:29:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.83,0:29:53.77,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Master, will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.77,0:29:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With these things I can make it all. {\alphaFF\t(1189,1189,\alpha0)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you small proprietress.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.58,0:30:01.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both the proprietress and the great-proprietress are relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.78,0:30:06.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Using cucumbers, kamaboko and avocados for the raw fishless spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.38,0:30:10.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the homepa spreads with fish are also done.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.52,0:30:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you did so well today Yuna I will
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.06,0:30:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,make you the food you want to eat the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.39,0:30:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make that sushi for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.56,0:30:23.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How nice. Eating sushi at the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:27.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Uni, ikura, toro or eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.94,0:30:29.61,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Horse mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.61,0:30:30.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.81,0:30:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.44,0:30:35.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The local mackerel around here is famous for its fattiness and flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.98,0:30:38.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the master's priceless ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.02,0:30:39.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.82,0:30:44.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a connoisseur's way of eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.65,0:30:44.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,How refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.52,0:30:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.76,0:30:51.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to be the daughter of a sushi chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.43,0:30:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.20,0:30:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tough errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.73,0:30:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really made me anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.84,0:31:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534.857,605.085)}Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.84,0:31:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(969.428,504.407)}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.84,0:31:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end even the mother went.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.21,0:31:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really remarkable {\alphaFF\t(1184,1184,\alpha0)}how verbal she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.08,0:31:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Avocados. Avocados.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.98,0:31:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was amazed at how the mother said "You won't lose"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.32,0:31:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,, cause it made her kid excited and really turned on a switch in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.49,0:31:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ebizou, to your children
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.36,0:31:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when you need to motivate them,{\alphaFF\t(917,917,\alpha0)} \Ndo you have a way to switch them on?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.29,0:31:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.40,0:31:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(519.75,101)}TN: Before his wife died of breast cancer they spent her last 25 days together with their kids at their home. He has blogged about those last 25 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.33,0:31:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you motivate them {\alphaFF\t(2186,2186,\alpha0)}then it will only work for 25 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.20,0:31:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you keep doing it{\alphaFF\t(2020,2020,\alpha0)} it eventually loses its effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.93,0:31:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it only for those rare occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.97,0:31:37.11,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965.7,487.4)\alphaFF\t(0,319,\alpha0\t(5824,0,\alphaFF))}Kangen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.67,0:31:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it only works for about a week after opening day.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.24,0:31:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to come from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.41,0:31:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't overshoot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.95,0:31:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want him to also learn how to handle even the days that don't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.45,0:31:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell him that many people came to watch the play
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.36,0:31:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and if he does fail
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.89,0:31:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he will sense it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.56,0:32:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So on those days he will cry tears of disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.20,0:32:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's really introspective about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.23,0:32:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.07,0:32:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of courage to self-reflect like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.91,0:32:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotou when it comes to a motivation boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I treat him with a movie and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.94,0:32:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.28,0:32:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give him candy to encourge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.08,0:32:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Mikitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.28,0:32:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We do the opposite with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.09,0:32:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lion King style.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.45,0:32:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2628,0,\alphaFF)}If my kid falls I say: Get back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.29,0:32:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.76,0:32:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When he says: "I don't want to go today."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.16,0:32:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.26,0:32:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say during those times?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.90,0:32:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By saying you won't go today does it mean you will never ever go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.30,0:32:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he says: "Yes, I will go." \NAnd he follows up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.11,0:32:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's indeed how{\alphaFF\t(984,984,\alpha0)} mothers are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.18,0:32:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They will say: "No good. Go right away."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.55,0:32:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I am by their side and say: "I will give you candy."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.85,0:32:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife says: "Oy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.42,0:32:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so true. You really understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.35,0:33:01.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Later in this program: The Japanese Rugby team captain Tanaka's son will go on his first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.96,0:33:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Collagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.96,0:33:05.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Collagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.53,0:33:09.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can he purchase collagen for his papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.37,0:33:12.60,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chicken thighs, {\alphaFF\t(1885,1885,\alpha0)}please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.60,0:33:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.44,0:33:18.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tanaka papa's breath is taken away all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.58,0:33:23.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Seto Inland Sea is full of delicious fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.81,0:33:27.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Akashi sea bream in the harmony of Harima's open seas and oysters from Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.09,0:33:32.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The second largest island in the Seto Inland Sea is Shoudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.49,0:33:36.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here there is a big fishmonger called Gyoden.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.36,0:33:39.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's almost like a fish market.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.20,0:33:42.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today they have Japanese amberjacks, blue crabs, rockfish and conger eel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.63,0:33:44.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, the octupus is escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.70,0:33:45.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,It fell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.80,0:33:46.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everything here is fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.64,0:33:50.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Every morning they bring the desired fish to the market
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.91,0:33:54.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and when they close the entire selection has been sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.21,0:33:58.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have such a passion for fish they take the trouble to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.78,0:34:01.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's no one better than this master.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.08,0:34:02.95,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a nice smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.99,0:34:06.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother cherishes his little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.06,0:34:11.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Previously he would beg to be fed and clothed and being babied.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.43,0:34:19.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But now his mother scolds him: "You are not a baby anymore. You are a big brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.90,0:34:23.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother should be able to go to the fishmonger by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.01,0:34:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rintarou, {\alphaFF\t(1919,1919,\alpha0)}can you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.11,0:34:27.68,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,By myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.98,0:34:29.51,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Now way I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.51,0:34:31.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Didn't he become a big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.35,0:34:34.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.32,0:34:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.95,0:34:36.65,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I absolutely can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.65,0:34:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy who can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.92,0:34:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You absolutely can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.16,0:34:42.26,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Because it's too embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.26,0:34:44.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother is too shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.29,0:34:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rintarou yesterday you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.96,0:34:51.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he became 4 he has started feeling really shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.33,0:34:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.34,0:34:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right since you are baby, Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.54,0:34:58.48,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm not a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.48,0:35:01.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This spring he happily entered giraffe class in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.81,0:35:03.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm not a baby anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.91,0:35:08.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm a big brother who can do things by myself and take care of my baby sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.42,0:35:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.32,0:35:12.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,322,\alpha0)\pos(540,1004.2)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.22,0:35:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do about Chinatsu? {\alphaFF\t(2693,2693,\alpha0)}She's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.99,0:35:21.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu is crying from hunger. {\alphaFF\t(2627,2627,\alpha0)}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.33,0:35:24.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright, I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.67,0:35:25.74,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's manning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.57,0:35:26.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.24,0:35:32.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For his hungry little sister
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.44,0:35:35.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he's getting white fleshed fish at Gyoden
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.25,0:35:39.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,grilling fish of the season and squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.02,0:35:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go. {\alphaFF\t(1485,1485,\alpha0)}Do y' bes'.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.68,0:35:43.72,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Do m' best'.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.59,0:35:44.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.05,0:35:47.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he's no longer a baby he better do his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.39,0:35:50.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's tough being a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.06,0:35:57.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Across the bridge it smells of soft rush reeds
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.37,0:35:59.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a tatami shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.17,0:36:02.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gyoden is down this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.31,0:36:05.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop sign is within sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.34,0:36:08.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.61,0:36:11.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,No way I can lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.01,0:36:14.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's getting fish of the season, squid and white-fleshed fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.88,0:36:19.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For Chinatsu's first weaning meal, they will feed her white-fleshed fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.56,0:36:21.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has arrived at Gyoden.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.56,0:36:22.83,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.19,0:36:27.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Squid and delicious fish please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.13,0:36:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for delicious fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.10,0:36:30.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's true that fish of the season are delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.63,0:36:32.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's good today?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.74,0:36:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your mother say grilled{\alphaFF\t(2686,2686,\alpha0)} or boiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.04,0:36:41.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Grilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.61,0:36:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She said grilled?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.31,0:36:43.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The recommendation changes based on preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.78,0:36:47.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A fishmonger that even sells to high-end restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.72,0:36:50.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What grilling fish do you recommend today?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.85,0:36:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want this one? {\alphaFF\t(1526,1526,\alpha0)}A pink colored fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.59,0:36:54.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cherry anthias.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.52,0:36:56.86,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This one is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.96,0:37:00.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What is it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.13,0:37:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sea bream.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.90,0:37:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you want this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.03,0:37:03.27,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.27,0:37:05.54,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And squid, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.50,0:37:09.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a young squid. {\alphaFF\t(1225,1225,\alpha0)}Meaty and with a sweetness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.71,0:37:14.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And perhaps some tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.78,0:37:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluefin tuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.04,0:37:17.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His beloved bluefin tuna is rarely available here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.01,0:37:19.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The store boasts mostly local seafood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.01,0:37:22.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know about largehead hairtails.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.75,0:37:23.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.19,0:37:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this shrimp?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.62,0:37:25.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Still can't eat those.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.96,0:37:27.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since Chinatsu is still a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.12,0:37:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about this crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.39,0:37:30.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Also can't eat crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.43,0:37:34.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was told that they can't feed her crustaceans yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.86,0:37:35.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,He understands all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.60,0:37:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.67,0:37:39.87,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And white-fleshed fish too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.97,0:37:39.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, for Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.70,0:37:47.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since the sea bream is already a white-fleshed fish he ponders his next choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.81,0:37:52.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for an even whiter fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.35,0:37:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An even whiter fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.42,0:37:54.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,Makes sense to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.95,0:37:55.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even with her fish expertise the old lady is struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.42,0:37:58.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A white one with no colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.99,0:38:01.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's looking for one that is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.92,0:38:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A fish without a color? This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.43,0:38:05.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Red tonguesole.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.46,0:38:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.53,0:38:09.80,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But there's color on its backside.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:12.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.13,0:38:12.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.57,0:38:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nitpicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.37,0:38:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.04,0:38:18.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But there's color on its backside.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.31,0:38:21.64,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.21,0:38:21.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's still a white-fleshed fish, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.64,0:38:23.51,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's nitpicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.68,0:38:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it becomes white.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You peel the skin off and it's white beneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.65,0:38:30.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.35,0:38:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to make it white for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.69,0:38:34.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.22,0:38:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.99,0:38:38.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But Rintarou really wants to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.39,0:38:40.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's curious how she can make it white.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.39,0:38:44.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Since I'm in giraffe class I want to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.17,0:38:46.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A morbid curiousity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.00,0:38:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It will become white.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.41,0:38:51.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's his first time seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.17,0:38:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.81,0:38:54.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Removing the darkened skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.34,0:38:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.28,0:38:57.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And it slips off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.55,0:39:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}See, it become white. {\alphaFF\t(2120,2120,\alpha0)}Isn't it good? It's white on both sides now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.78,0:39:00.08,Studio,,0,0,0,,How pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.49,0:39:04.35,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But please cut off the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.99,0:39:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut off the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.92,0:39:07.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's making demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.62,0:39:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do the next one Rintarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.09,0:39:11.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The cute fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.69,0:39:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.50,0:39:15.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's filleting the grilling fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.53,0:39:19.84,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Poor fish looks in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.90,0:39:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.84,0:39:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.80,0:39:22.67,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.67,0:39:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.84,0:39:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will watch {\alphaFF\t(1121,1121,\alpha0)}since Rintarou {\alphaFF\t(2122,2122,\alpha0)}is in giraffe class.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.48,0:39:31.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His pride from being in giraffe class has strengthened Rintarou who usually loves being babied.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.25,0:39:33.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's staring at it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.82,0:39:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I split it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.79,0:39:39.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He wasn't ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.15,0:39:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.02,0:39:40.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But giving it his all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.16,0:39:44.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Rintarou farted.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.33,0:39:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You just made a toot?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.53,0:39:47.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,The best.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.73,0:39:47.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.53,0:39:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.87,0:39:51.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm wet for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.73,0:39:54.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.64,0:39:54.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having overcome his embarrassment
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:56.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he has succeeded with the errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.57,0:39:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.24,0:40:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how much it amounts to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.84,0:40:02.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Time to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.85,0:40:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.78,0:40:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,have this dried fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.38,0:40:05.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The master has been observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.98,0:40:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.92,0:40:09.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And wants to give him delicious curry as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.69,0:40:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry. Do you dislike curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.09,0:40:12.72,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I dislike curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.72,0:40:15.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for this in your busy schedule, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.66,0:40:17.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,It was a nice offer, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.49,0:40:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine with only 2000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.66,0:40:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,2000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.43,0:40:22.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He bought all this for 2000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.27,0:40:24.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It has been greatly discounted by the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.27,0:40:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.10,0:40:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care. {\alphaFF\t(1759,1759,\alpha0)}Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.84,0:40:33.88,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Until next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.28,0:40:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.08,0:40:37.38,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.38,0:40:39.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a splendid shopping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.18,0:40:43.65,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(3160,0,\alphaFF)}The town of sun rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.19,0:40:49.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it will be sunny tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.96,0:40:56.30,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The paprika flowers are in bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.17,0:41:06.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mood has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.94,0:41:10.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He crosses the bridge in a sunny mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.51,0:41:12.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The anxious one is his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:14.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She keeps looking at the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.47,0:41:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.27,0:41:34.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's his mothers voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.47,0:41:35.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. {\alphaFF\t(887,887,\alpha0)}Above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.11,0:41:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.11,0:41:40.34,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.34,0:41:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(1926,0,\alphaFF)}It's just a bit further.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.62,0:41:49.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,She looks delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.39,0:41:58.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(5425,0,\alphaFF)}The paprika flowers are in bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.56,0:42:00.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please have a look at this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.30,0:42:07.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please look at his posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.14,0:42:10.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He opens the doors with all his might.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.47,0:42:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2693,0,\alphaFF)}Welcome back. {\alphaFF\t(1159,1159,\alpha0)\t(2693,0,\alphaFF)}You went? Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.68,0:42:15.04,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.65,0:42:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.28,0:42:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu is delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.08,0:42:22.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He did his best for Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.19,0:42:24.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Boiling the red tonguesole
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.75,0:42:28.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,grilling the seabream in soy sauce and serving the squid raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.39,0:42:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(70.875,395)}Father
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.39,0:42:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.66,0:42:33.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of course the Shoudo island-born father loves his fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.70,0:42:37.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His first meal was also a white-fleshed fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.73,0:42:42.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is also Chinatsu's first taste of white fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.94,0:42:41.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.71,0:42:45.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Your brother bought these.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.11,0:42:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now able to go on errands
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.14,0:42:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,who is the big brother{\alphaFF\t(2127,2127,\alpha0)} in the giraffe class.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.41,0:42:53.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Surely it's Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.85,0:42:56.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a magnificent big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.72,0:42:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.70,0:43:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.17,0:43:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults speak within a in-the-know context
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.07,0:43:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but white-fleshed fish isn't conveyed well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.01,0:43:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He heard it as simply white fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.18,0:43:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In general, with small children - like with kamaboko earlier -
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.25,0:43:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of them think that kamabo swims in the ocean like that paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.75,0:43:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So he will try to avert his eyes as the sea bream is being cut
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.76,0:43:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and while feeling sorry for its pain he will still look on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.86,0:43:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.20,0:43:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a big brother so I've often noticed that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.37,0:43:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,a younger sister usually only sees their strong side.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.41,0:43:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he was on his way home his attitude changed positively.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.51,0:43:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So to see the troubles of an older brother
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.75,0:43:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,really made me emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.95,0:44:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of brothers... Amami.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.02,0:44:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true that I have both a big and a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.69,0:44:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I really thought about how the brother did his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.19,0:44:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We often went to the ocean near Toyama during the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.23,0:44:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One time it poured down. {\alphaFF\t(2422,2422,\alpha0)}And I was so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.90,0:44:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared that I started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.73,0:44:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We were both huddled under a bath towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.90,0:44:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and said "you can have it".
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.94,0:44:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(533.25,999)}How gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.84,0:44:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My older brother was surely cold too
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.91,0:44:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and this segment made me think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.91,0:44:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.71,0:44:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.25,0:44:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moved by your lovely story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.68,0:44:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{}You are not crying during a segment but {\alphaFF\t(826,826,\alpha0)}during our talks in between!?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.22,0:44:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They sound so gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.79,0:44:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.46,0:44:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,1005.8)}I can't believe that this happened{\alphaFF\t(885,885,\alpha0)} during our talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.03,0:44:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And for our next errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.59,0:44:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A thrifty boy on an adventure to man up for his beloved father.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.63,0:44:58.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In Aizu, the town of Kitakata which is homophonic with Northway and is famous for their Kitakata ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.24,0:45:00.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With its doughy and voluminous noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.11,0:45:04.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With its thick noodles covered in broth. It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.81,0:45:09.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When speaking of Kitakata ramen, the soup can vary from seafood broth to animal broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.52,0:45:11.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From light flavor to strong flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.59,0:45:14.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this town with a population of just under 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.36,0:45:16.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are over 100 joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.23,0:45:23.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}And this joint that's been operational for 36 years is run by a father who wants to put their child to an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.70,0:45:27.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who from Sendai has taken over the joint just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.27,0:45:33.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This fighter who is wearing the same clothes as the owner is the 3 years and 9 months old Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.08,0:45:35.08,Studio,,0,0,0,,3 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.88,0:45:39.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But at home where the owner is simply papa {\alphaFF\t(551,551,\alpha0)}Ao is treated sweetly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.82,0:45:44.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But her mother has raised his older siblings with tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.12,0:45:47.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But even she has a sweet spot for Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.62,0:45:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he's the youngest {\alphaFF\t(1893,1893,\alpha0)}and just about cute
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.46,0:45:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but treat him with cuteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.73,0:46:02.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's always looking at his brothers and sisters and is perfectly capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.04,0:46:06.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He helps out with various things even cooking. However....
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.98,0:46:10.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's still drinking milk from a bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.28,0:46:13.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He likes it too much to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.95,0:46:19.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ao has looked up to his father since he became a restaurant owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.92,0:46:22.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He wants to be cool like his father and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.73,0:46:26.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their home is just behind the joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.53,0:46:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao, it's time for you to put on your work clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.43,0:46:34.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Getting dressed for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.77,0:46:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.81,0:46:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the face. He's ready for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.28,0:46:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when we talked about what type of ramen kids would like?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.08,0:46:48.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They discussed it yesterday with the owner
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.32,0:46:50.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to change the children's ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.45,0:46:52.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They brainstormed on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.62,0:46:55.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They would need some petit noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.22,0:47:00.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Currently the freebie is some candy but what if they change it to toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.79,0:47:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640.125,829.8)}- Kamen Rider toy \N- Stickers
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.20,0:47:02.00,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Would be lovely with toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.00,0:47:03.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will adopt Ao's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.87,0:47:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(513,55)}Gachapon: Capsule-toy from a vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.87,0:47:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa said that it would be nice with a gachapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.07,0:47:10.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is usually told not to get gachapon by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.04,0:47:13.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but this time it will be his errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.34,0:47:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We want an {\alphaFF\t(1758,1758,\alpha0)}Anpanman gachapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.45,0:47:19.88,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Eh? Not getting a Kamen Rider toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.88,0:47:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But only boys will be happy with a Kamen Rider toy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.15,0:47:26.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see, equal rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.82,0:47:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.72,0:47:29.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A gachapon errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.03,0:47:32.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But you need them for your experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.63,0:47:36.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First he will bring an apron to his father's work place.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.07,0:47:38.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Experiment for three.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.00,0:47:40.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The petit noodles is at the noodle maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.77,0:47:46.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was asked to get gachapon from the supermarket and Anpanman kamaboko and milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.77,0:47:48.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's only 3 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.21,0:47:50.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they need 3 toys he can do it thrice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.21,0:47:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember to loudly proclaim \N"Thank you for your hard work, owner".
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.62,0:47:56.19,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.19,0:47:59.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because his father is the owner when he's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.02,0:48:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.02,0:48:01.26,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.60,0:48:16.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today he's on an errand so he enters through the backdoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.37,0:48:20.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's always told the he can't just enter the store to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.58,0:48:25.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But today, he's wearing his work apron so he's free to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.85,0:48:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Order up!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.39,0:48:33.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The loud voice of his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.42,0:48:35.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop is full of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.26,0:48:37.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The clanging of utensils.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.49,0:48:40.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,325,\alpha50)}Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.70,0:48:42.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.77,0:48:44.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here is his fathers' apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.07,0:48:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.77,0:48:49.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father makes sure he knows what to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.77,0:48:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.21,0:48:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going shopping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.78,0:48:54.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.41,0:48:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you are getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.28,0:48:59.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Gachapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.78,0:49:03.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected his head is full of toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.89,0:49:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,3 petit noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.02,0:49:07.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's petit noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.59,0:49:11.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These short noodles are ideal for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.63,0:49:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.90,0:49:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.46,0:49:16.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.10,0:49:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can exit through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.30,0:49:20.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Feels like he's only heading for the toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.24,0:49:25.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Things already look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.41,0:49:30.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,Did he become homesick?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.41,0:49:34.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As if stuck to the ground {\alphaFF\t(2426,2426,\alpha0)}his feet stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.55,0:49:36.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.85,0:49:39.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's not moving a bit in front of the joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.89,0:49:45.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's expected from a 3 year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.63,0:49:48.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The joint is blocking the view to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.57,0:49:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's still over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.84,0:49:55.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father can see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.14,0:49:59.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been looking on for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.54,0:50:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.31,0:50:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(3092,0,\alphaFF)}Aren't you going shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.92,0:50:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao, you are a boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.55,0:50:14.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Ao who wants to be a man like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.89,0:50:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You will go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.13,0:50:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just keep standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.19,0:50:22.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father, {\alphaFF\t(1127,1127,\alpha0)}told him once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.63,0:50:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.73,0:50:26.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,Dad's gonna cry too!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.10,0:50:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(3161,0,\alphaFF)}Can you go and do your best?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.07,0:50:31.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,489,\alpha0)\pos(540,1004.2)\t(2191,0,\alphaFF)}Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.74,0:50:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.04,0:50:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be watching from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.08,0:50:36.21,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.68,0:50:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best. {\alphaFF\t(1021,1021,\alpha0)}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.52,0:50:42.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's told to do his best not as an instruction
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.95,0:50:44.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but as his fathers prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.95,0:50:48.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A prayer to make Ao strong and go forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.40,0:50:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's green. You can go. {\alphaFF\t(1185,1185,\alpha0)}Raise your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.87,0:50:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go. Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.57,0:51:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2055,0,\alphaFF)}Do your best Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.37,0:51:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it! {\alphaFF\t(924,924,\alpha0)}He crossed the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.18,0:51:08.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,His mother was also worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.58,0:51:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.71,0:51:16.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seems like his fathers and mothers prayers have come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.46,0:51:27.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they are making three meals he needs to get three toys and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.73,0:51:30.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On this street to the left is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.10,0:51:33.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the big supermarket with the toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.80,0:51:37.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait!? {\alphaFF\t(925,925,\alpha0)}He's crossing the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.34,0:51:40.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which means he's not getting the gachapon but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.44,0:51:43.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he's heading for the noodle maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.05,0:51:47.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Look at this face. He's not playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.02,0:51:51.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's making a serious face.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.16,0:52:03.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The noodles he needs to get are shorter so that kids can easily eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.00,0:52:07.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This place is where they get all of their noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.57,0:52:11.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have started allowing regular customers to purchase items here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.04,0:52:14.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They make the noodles inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.58,0:52:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2620,0,\alphaFF)}Good day.{\alphaFF\t(919,919,\alpha0)\t(2620,0,\alphaFF)} Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.51,0:52:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.65,0:52:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come by yourself? {\alphaFF\t(1386,1386,\alpha0)}Are you on an errand?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.08,0:52:23.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been giving it his all so far but...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.72,0:52:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.39,0:52:28.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.62,0:52:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.33,0:52:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? {\alphaFF\t(1520,1520,\alpha0)}Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.96,0:52:34.46,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.53,0:52:37.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh!? {\alphaFF\t(1289,1289,\alpha0)}What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.37,0:52:38.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Three petit noodles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.03,0:52:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.87,0:52:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.24,0:52:44.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe he will remember after a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.24,0:52:46.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.58,0:52:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you been told to purchase?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.08,0:52:55.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(356,356,\alpha50)}Thick noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.15,0:52:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534.375,1003)}Thick noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.38,0:52:56.39,Studio,,0,0,0,,Thick noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.08,0:52:58.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He realizes immediately that it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.89,0:52:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.79,0:53:01.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha50}Thick noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.59,0:53:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thick noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.06,0:53:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your mama say thick noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.86,0:53:04.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Petit noodles and thick noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.66,0:53:06.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to differentiate for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.96,0:53:09.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Surely the owner can work with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.20,0:53:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.17,0:53:14.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was not able to let out his voice inside
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.77,0:53:17.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but he knows what to say when leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.44,0:53:20.91,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.91,0:53:23.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has more confidence now that he has the noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.92,0:53:30.59,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yaay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.72,0:53:30.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mood is improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.59,0:53:32.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yaay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.82,0:53:34.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yayay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.69,0:53:37.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe his mood is too over the top now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.13,0:53:42.16,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The gachapon is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.36,0:53:46.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,My mama said to get gachapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.13,0:53:49.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Three. {\alphaFF\t(1561,1561,\alpha0)}You should only get three.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.37,0:53:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If he gets a Kamen Rider gachapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.81,0:53:59.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's usually told he can't but today he's told to get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.95,0:54:02.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You rarely hear something this delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.25,0:54:04.42,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,There's also this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.59,0:54:05.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.69,0:54:10.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He wants to get the Kamen Rider but {\alphaFF\t(1854,1854,\alpha0)}he's holding it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.03,0:54:11.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Today it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.33,0:54:12.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.43,0:54:14.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even girls would be delighted by Anpanman.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.96,0:54:17.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's only 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.83,0:54:19.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.27,0:54:22.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.67,0:54:24.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Two more to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.65,0:54:32.51,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.51,0:54:34.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.15,0:54:35.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.88,0:54:37.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.35,0:54:38.89,Studio,,0,0,0,,"But?"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.62,0:54:41.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Since when I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.09,0:54:44.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,do it multiple times mama scolds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.16,0:54:47.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,Hit a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.89,0:54:49.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's different today since you were asked to.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.67,0:54:54.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's afraid that he will be scolded if he does it a second time but he does it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.94,0:54:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Since today is an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.41,0:54:59.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Needs three.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.18,0:55:05.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's fine. {\alphaFF\t(1052,1052,\alpha0)}He was asked to get three so one more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.35,0:55:10.72,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2057,0,\alphaFF)}I better not do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.72,0:55:15.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though he was asked to get three he could only do it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.36,0:55:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.93,0:55:19.63,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Next up is the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.63,0:55:23.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He needs to get milk but he doesn't know where to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.60,0:55:26.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The easiest way is to ask the shop attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.84,0:55:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.01,0:55:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.24,0:55:32.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.01,0:55:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.11,0:55:35.11,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.78,0:55:35.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was able to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.68,0:55:35.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.01,0:55:38.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady is taking him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.48,0:55:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of milk? Big? Small?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.48,0:55:40.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.62,0:55:42.58,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.55,0:55:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.85,0:55:46.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He wants to drink a lot so he's getting the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.02,0:55:48.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.26,0:55:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What else do you want to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.93,0:55:50.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.39,0:55:53.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was also asked to get Anpanman kamaboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.80,0:55:56.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.10,0:55:58.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, they passed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.13,0:56:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you purchase previously?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.97,0:56:03.07,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.14,0:56:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.61,0:56:10.21,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.58,0:56:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to put in the ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.21,0:56:12.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What goes well with ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.45,0:56:15.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We have a lot already.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.65,0:56:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.95,0:56:17.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since it's a ramen joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.72,0:56:19.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.76,0:56:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(542.25,51)}Both naruto and imitation crab are types of kamaboko (steamed fish paste).
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.12,0:56:20.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Imitation crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.22,0:56:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about putting this in ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.92,0:56:24.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He loves imitation crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.59,0:56:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to put it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.13,0:56:25.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.53,0:56:27.70,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's original.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.86,0:56:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two types of gachapon. {\alphaFF\t(3226,3226,\alpha0)}\NIs this for playing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.40,0:56:35.30,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is for the children's ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.97,0:56:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.14,0:56:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a freebie for the {\alphaFF\t(1121,1121,\alpha0)}children's ramen set?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.44,0:56:41.54,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,1004.2)}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.08,0:56:41.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.54,0:56:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.08,0:56:44.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady is sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.08,0:56:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A ramen joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.11,0:56:46.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The name of the store is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.95,0:56:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Raiyuu ramen joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.82,0:56:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so? I always go there to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.92,0:56:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.55,0:56:53.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's a regular.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.76,0:56:57.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa is doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.06,0:57:00.06,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,He's making delicious ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.46,0:57:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He is, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.23,0:57:03.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been observing {\alphaFF\t(1888,1888,\alpha0)}his fathers ramen making.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.83,0:57:08.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The work of the second generation owner. {\alphaFF\t(2192,2192,\alpha0)}Proud of his cool dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.61,0:57:13.58,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Carrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.58,0:57:17.58,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A heave {\alphaFF\t(2619,2619,\alpha0)}and a ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.68,0:57:19.88,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's heavy but
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.22,0:57:22.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's heavy but he's carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.49,0:57:24.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Can't hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.69,0:57:26.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can't hold it but he is carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.66,0:57:29.66,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Feels like I can't carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.72,0:57:30.73,Studio,,0,0,0,,Feels like he can't carry it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.36,0:57:35.36,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What should I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.43,0:57:38.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While he complains he does have spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.23,0:57:41.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's heavy and I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.17,0:57:44.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You're not reckless {\alphaFF\t(1522,1522,\alpha0)}you are clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.34,0:57:47.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Break time. {\alphaFF\t(955,955,\alpha0)}Break time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.28,0:57:51.65,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.65,0:57:55.02,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama said that {\alphaFF\t(1920,1920,\alpha0)}I should
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.02,0:57:57.15,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,put it in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.15,0:57:58.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.99,0:58:03.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. {\alphaFF\t(1720,1720,\alpha0)}He remembered what his mother said.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.56,0:58:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.39,0:58:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know not to peek but I can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.66,0:58:11.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.13,0:58:14.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The thoughts of a parent who can only pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.94,0:58:18.91,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,924.2)}Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.14,0:58:19.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After putting it in the bag both his hands are free to.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.34,0:58:22.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.98,0:58:25.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He feels lighter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.46,0:58:37.19,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.23,0:58:41.46,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will rest at home. {\alphaFF\t(2986,2986,\alpha0)}I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.40,0:58:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.33,0:58:46.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will inform his mother first.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.90,0:58:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.41,0:58:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.11,0:58:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was heavy, right? Mama will help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.78,0:59:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped. You truly helped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.82,0:59:02.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He better take it to the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.95,0:59:06.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time he's making a grand entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.05,0:59:08.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This face.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.46,0:59:13.66,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa, {\alphaFF\t(1188,1188,\alpha0)}ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.49,0:59:13.66,Default,,0,0,80,,Did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.53,0:59:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought some?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.66,0:59:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the Anpanman kamaboko
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.20,0:59:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.47,0:59:21.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.10,0:59:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped out.{\alphaFF\t(724,724,\alpha0)} Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.31,0:59:29.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he bought thick noodles {\alphaFF\t(2019,2019,\alpha0)}he made the soup a bit thicker to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.78,0:59:32.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With imitation crab that kids love.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.08,0:59:34.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Might be cuter this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.18,0:59:38.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Valuing the opinion of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.75,0:59:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.59,0:59:41.86,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.86,0:59:44.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's an okay if Ao says it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.73,0:59:49.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a children's ramen who will excitedly anticipate what type of toy is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.43,0:59:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What you bought I...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.73,0:59:55.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will take a big gulp today especially since he bought the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.20,0:59:55.07,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(172.125,75)}He can hardly lift it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.91,1:00:01.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today will be his last day with the baby bottle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.71,1:00:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2824,0,\alphaFF)}How cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.24,1:00:04.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,He does look cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.32,1:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The hesitant way he was holding the 100 yen coin.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.12,1:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid to put it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.56,1:00:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that he was standing in front of the joint for 20 minutes. {\alphaFF\t(4458,4458,\alpha0)}Made me teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.40,1:00:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me reflect on my own memories and brought back a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.27,1:00:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When boys {\alphaFF\t(755,755,\alpha0)}are able to clear just a single task
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.91,1:00:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and immediately celebrating it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.78,1:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that's such an endearing part about boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.91,1:00:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite his maturing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.65,1:00:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to celebrate it with {\alphaFF\t(618,618,\alpha0)}milk from the baby bottle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.58,1:00:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,911)}It was kinda cool. He just can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.99,1:00:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that just cool?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.49,1:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.59,1:00:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he shouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.79,1:00:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The next errand is with a girl but the premise is a sibling fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.62,1:01:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(884.25,201)}Fukushima ● Yamato city
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.70,1:01:02.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The C57 still runs in the northern part of Fukushima.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.00,1:01:05.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The house is near where the steam whistle can be heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.21,1:01:09.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Karin is the last child among the three friendly siblings.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.74,1:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358.875,237)}{\alphaFF\t(0,489,\alpha0)\fs34}Big sister
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.74,1:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(783,207)}{\alphaFF\t(0,489,\alpha0)\fs34}Big \Nbrother
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.74,1:01:10.68,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(438.75,1007)}{\alphaFF\t(0,489,\alpha0)}4 years 8 months
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.74,1:01:10.68,PurpleFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(371.25,821)}{\alphaFF\t(0,489,\alpha0)}Karin
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.84,1:01:15.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 weeks ago she ripped her big sisters playing cards which resulted in a huge fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.15,1:01:17.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She knew that she had done bad
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.75,1:01:23.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So she said that: "Karin will buy new cards with her own savings."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.53,1:01:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When she is determined to go she will go. I asked her where do you want to go
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.60,1:01:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and she said: "Icchan's cards."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.70,1:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked who was bad she said: "Karin".
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.50,1:01:37.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While her sister was playing Sevens
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.61,1:01:41.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Karin begged to get to play along
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.51,1:01:46.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was told no cause they were in the middle of a game.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.28,1:01:49.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She got mad and ripped a card.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.25,1:01:55.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No matter how much she apologized her sister did not forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.99,1:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.06,1:02:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the reason for the big fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.00,1:02:04.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They tried to fix it with tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.63,1:02:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She said: "I will never forgive you."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.50,1:02:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time she's gotten this mad {\alphaFF\t(1959,1959,\alpha0)}towards Karin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.91,1:02:14.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wants to go back to before she ripped the card.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.44,1:02:19.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I see. I could buy new cards with my savings."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.38,1:02:21.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what Karin thought of.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.02,1:02:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have two 1 yen coins.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.79,1:02:28.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She only has 2 yen?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.99,1:02:28.79,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ka~rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.62,1:02:30.23,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please lend me some money.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.23,1:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you will repay me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.19,1:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.93,1:02:34.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will borrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.23,1:02:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With five 100 yen coins {\alphaFF\t(1855,1855,\alpha0)}you can buy one pack of cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.20,1:02:40.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One pack of cards for 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.60,1:02:43.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother looked into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.27,1:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely wear your hood.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.84,1:02:47.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It has started raining a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.01,1:02:50.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If I don't hurry they will sell out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.41,1:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to wear your hood.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.72,1:02:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever feel lonely{\alphaFF\t(1920,1920,\alpha0)} then hug this charm tightly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.69,1:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama made this to protect you, Karin.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.96,1:03:05.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mom has made preparations
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.23,1:03:06.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A charm with a microphone inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.69,1:03:08.16,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,A good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.43,1:03:10.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her first time going shopping alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.43,1:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.84,1:03:18.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Wasn't she the one who wanted to go alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.81,1:03:18.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to go anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.74,1:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.91,1:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.58,1:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you anxious?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.68,1:03:31.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She noticed how lonely it will be to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.75,1:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be forgiven, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.22,1:03:34.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.39,1:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The whistle is blowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.59,1:03:39.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her expression changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.46,1:03:44.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The power of the C57's whistle.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.50,1:03:47.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which made Karin determined.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.30,1:03:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please depart with the steam locomotive.{\alphaFF\t(1892,1892,\alpha0)} You want to be forgiven, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.37,1:03:51.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.84,1:03:52.67,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.67,1:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.58,1:03:56.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will go and purchase cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.34,1:03:59.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And she's also getting her sisters favorite cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.28,1:04:01.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother gave her money for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.35,1:04:07.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On the way back she's also getting soba. Her sister will surely be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.75,1:04:08.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,Tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.29,1:04:10.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2756,0,\alphaFF)}Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.36,1:04:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,1005)}Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.69,1:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of the cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.03,1:04:12.89,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.89,1:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.56,1:04:14.83,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.23,1:04:15.63,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's going.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.83,1:04:16.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I better go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.63,1:04:20.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's going on her first errand with this sense of duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.44,1:04:25.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother truly believes that Karin is carrying such a conviction.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.91,1:04:28.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a determined expression.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.08,1:04:31.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No longer anxious. She's all good now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.08,1:05:03.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An expression full of a sense of duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.48,1:05:08.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cards are sold in the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.75,1:05:12.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was also told to get spring onion.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.89,1:05:18.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the main street of the town.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.16,1:05:22.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 days ago it was bustling with people due to the soba festival.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.26,1:05:27.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cake shop is also on this street.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.97,1:05:34.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seems like she's getting cake first?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.34,1:05:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. {\alphaFF\t(657,657,\alpha0)}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.18,1:05:37.51,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.51,1:05:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you by yourself? {\alphaFF\t(1925,1925,\alpha0)}What about your mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.58,1:05:42.05,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,At home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.05,1:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.62,1:05:47.09,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Two gâteau au chocolat, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.05,1:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gâteau au chocolat?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.09,1:05:48.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's purchasing two?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.09,1:05:53.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One is for her sister. {\alphaFF\t(1590,1590,\alpha0)}So the other is for herself?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.26,1:05:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will eat these gâteau au chocolat?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.70,1:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.80,1:06:02.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Icchan and {\alphaFF\t(3323,3323,\alpha0)}my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.57,1:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.50,1:06:06.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So she's getting one for her brother too?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.17,1:06:07.34,Studio,,0,0,0,,How kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.41,1:06:08.18,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please separate the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.18,1:06:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are giving both?{\alphaFF\t(851,851,\alpha0)} So you need two?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.58,1:06:12.51,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please separate the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.51,1:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you meant "separate" them? {\alphaFF\t(1426,1426,\alpha0)}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.15,1:06:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One more...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.15,1:06:20.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old man is putting them in separate boxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.82,1:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.56,1:06:26.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if she's getting two it's fine. {\alphaFF\t(1787,1787,\alpha0)}There's still money left for the cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.93,1:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of the cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.67,1:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the way?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.03,1:06:36.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Which way is Maruni?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.34,1:06:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruni? It's that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.04,1:06:38.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing that she could ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.44,1:06:40.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up is the most important thing - the cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.17,1:06:45.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rumor has spread like wildfire all over town that Karin is on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.35,1:06:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.85,1:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, {\alphaFF\t(1722,1722,\alpha0)}where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.85,1:06:52.65,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Maruni.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.45,1:06:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruni?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.65,1:06:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.19,1:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.99,1:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.49,1:06:56.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.22,1:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.79,1:06:59.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(177.75,79)}Loving the support.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.39,1:07:03.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone has already heard about the ripped up cards. {\alphaFF\t(3661,3661,\alpha0)}What a small world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.40,1:07:06.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has arrived at the shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.43,1:07:09.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they have some good cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.30,1:07:11.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.34,1:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Karin, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.44,1:07:14.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The store owner is her father's senior Tacchan.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.04,1:07:17.38,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Icchan, you see...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.55,1:07:21.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I've accidentally ripped her cards so I've come to buy new ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.68,1:07:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.55,1:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she get mad?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.68,1:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.72,1:07:27.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There was only one pack left.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.06,1:07:29.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tacchan has put it aside for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.56,1:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only these cards that cost 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.66,1:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.33,1:07:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.37,1:07:42.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These cards have some popular characters on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.97,1:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you rip Icchan's cards?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.11,1:07:48.94,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,We were fighting.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.44,1:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fighting?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.94,1:07:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Icchan became really upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.48,1:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you apologize?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.42,1:08:01.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To make her sister forgive her he wrapped it in {\alphaFF\t(2821,2821,\alpha0)}luxurious wrapping.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.06,1:08:03.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,She will surely be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.46,1:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3, 4.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.23,1:08:06.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's giving her a 100 yen discount.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.03,1:08:09.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I received this from mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.30,1:08:11.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No no. You borrowed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.20,1:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave you some? {\alphaFF\t(1923,1923,\alpha0)}How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.67,1:08:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.71,1:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.74,1:08:24.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The spring onions are in the food section.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.75,1:08:27.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's the errand her mother asked her to go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.18,1:08:30.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Spring onions for the soba she's making.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.35,1:08:32.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,Pretty amazing she remembers all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.85,1:08:34.56,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Found it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.56,1:08:37.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She found it right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.16,1:08:39.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are only for her father and grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.89,1:08:42.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Karin hasn't adjusted to the taste yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.63,1:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.53,1:08:46.60,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.60,1:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come to shop all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.27,1:08:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.71,1:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be 213 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.64,1:08:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work. {\alphaFF\t(923,923,\alpha0)}You are remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.81,1:09:00.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When she says hello {\alphaFF\t(1623,1623,\alpha0)}everyone returns the greeting with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.45,1:09:04.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tacchan has been watching her the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.32,1:09:06.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,How kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.92,1:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.53,1:09:13.73,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a nice town.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.73,1:09:15.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,How lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.13,1:09:20.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has bought the cards, the cake and the spring onions.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.37,1:09:23.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up is the homemade soba.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.64,1:09:25.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,Many things to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.14,1:09:27.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone is still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.54,1:09:31.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Every face is familiar.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.31,1:09:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you purchase?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.25,1:09:34.88,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Spring onions.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.88,1:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring onions.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.38,1:09:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you heading now?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.12,1:09:39.12,Studio,,0,0,0,,She remembers.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.25,1:09:39.12,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,150,,Soba.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.79,1:09:44.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's also someone on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.13,1:09:51.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old man from the cake shop was also worried so he's been watching from the outside the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.73,1:09:52.33,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.80,1:09:54.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The people of this town are watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.54,1:09:57.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So it will be fine even if she's by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.81,1:10:00.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She won't feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.34,1:10:04.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here at Kyoudoukan you can find the restaurant Soba Dojo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.71,1:10:08.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a place to polish your soba making skills.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.18,1:10:11.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her fathers junior, Tadayoshi, should be here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.42,1:10:16.56,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I've come to get soba.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.56,1:10:17.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is Tadayoshi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.89,1:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be making the soba now. {\alphaFF\t(2559,2559,\alpha0)}Do you want to come and watch?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.96,1:10:24.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,From scratch? That's quite something.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.70,1:10:25.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will be making it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.40,1:10:29.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since she came all the way he will show her how he makes it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.14,1:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is buckwheat soba. {\alphaFF\t(2120,2120,\alpha0)}See it's greenish?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.84,1:10:35.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So buckwheat soba is greenish.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.08,1:10:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now turn this into noodles.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.85,1:10:43.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The principal occupation of Tadayoshi is pottery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.52,1:10:47.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here in Yamato they have a soba-making workshop for non-professionals
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.82,1:10:51.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,where you can get certified for soba-making.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.46,1:10:55.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tadayoshi is so good he won the title of master in a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.76,1:10:56.50,Studio,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.30,1:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like soba?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.63,1:10:57.53,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.97,1:11:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And papa also loves soba, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.17,1:11:04.71,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And grandma. {\alphaFF\t(2488,2488,\alpha0)}And my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.20,1:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,997)}Grandmother too?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.60,1:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,997)}And your brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.87,1:11:06.47,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And Icchan too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.47,1:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone loves it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.04,1:11:09.84,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,No, my mom hates it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.05,1:11:12.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.68,1:11:16.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not that she hates it but she prefers rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.29,1:11:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What else did you buy today beside spring onion?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.86,1:11:22.69,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.69,1:11:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought cake? {\alphaFF\t(1189,1189,\alpha0)}Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.56,1:11:28.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Tadayoshi and Icchan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.76,1:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.56,1:11:32.60,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I bought it for Tadayoshi and Icchan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.60,1:11:34.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her "brother" was Tadayoshi?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.77,1:11:39.91,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Since you always do your best making soba.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.47,1:11:40.51,Studio,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.87,1:11:42.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tadayoshi is gleaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.11,1:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.68,1:11:48.22,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Icchan's Minion cards were ripped.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.22,1:11:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who ripped them?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.42,1:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, you ripped them?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.65,1:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And as an apology {\alphaFF\t(1027,1027,\alpha0)}you are giving new ones to Icchan? How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.46,1:12:01.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's time to cut.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.80,1:12:08.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is not something an amateur can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.31,1:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.67,1:12:16.14,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.58,1:12:16.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nothing but a pro.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.44,1:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.11,1:12:20.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.91,1:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(542.25,995)}Thank you.{\alphaFF\t(558,558,\alpha0)} You bought this for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.55,1:12:23.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The gâteau au chocolat she bought for Tadayoshiku.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.29,1:12:27.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he's not charging, this will be his reward.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.02,1:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.02,1:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please smile a bit more.{\alphaFF\t(2361,2361,\alpha0)} It's so delicious. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.96,1:12:35.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(543.375,1001)}Karin is also gleaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.60,1:12:36.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,She really is gleaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.50,1:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.86,1:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this to your mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.67,1:12:40.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.57,1:12:43.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's enough for all six in the family.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.08,1:13:00.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's 4 o'clock and we will be hearing that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.16,1:13:02.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,There is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.89,1:13:07.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A town where the whistle of the steam locomotive echoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.73,1:13:11.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even during tough times or when she wants to cry it suddenly changes her mood.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.70,1:13:14.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's no longer raining.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.57,1:13:17.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's walking with power.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.47,1:13:22.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother did say: "Once she's set on something then she will do it."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.51,1:13:25.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The figure of her mother can be seen in the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.28,1:13:28.35,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's on the verge of tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.08,1:13:32.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has spotted Karin coming from the direction of the soba shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.95,1:13:36.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's properly carrying the soba for six.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.66,1:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.70,1:13:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home Karin.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.53,1:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.47,1:13:47.10,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.33,1:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.97,1:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go to Tadayoshi-kun's place?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.41,1:13:55.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She even gave him cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.01,1:13:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(2189,0,\alphaFF)}You really did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.35,1:14:00.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,This is for Icchan.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.98,1:14:02.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cake for her sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.32,1:14:07.72,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And Icchan's cards {\alphaFF\t(2988,2988,\alpha0)}are inside this bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.72,1:14:09.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A new set of cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.16,1:14:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in stock?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.80,1:14:11.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.36,1:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You must go with these and {\alphaFF\t(1922,1922,\alpha0)}apologize so that she will forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.53,1:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You did will on your trip. {\alphaFF\t(1758,1758,\alpha0)}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.80,1:14:23.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if her sister forgave her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.64,1:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.14,1:14:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.21,1:14:27.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the big sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.54,1:14:31.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will she able to properly apologize to her big sister?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.75,1:14:35.82,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please come here. {\alphaFF\t(1285,1285,\alpha0)}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.72,1:14:39.79,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Icchan.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.95,1:14:46.66,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the other day {\alphaFF\t(2496,2496,\alpha0)}when I ripped the Minion cards.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.69,1:14:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,1003)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.79,1:14:48.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was able to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.50,1:14:50.40,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Please hurry and open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.40,1:14:53.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they only had these she's curious if she will like them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.64,1:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They are cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.54,1:14:59.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.27,1:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.34,1:15:02.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her big sister loves these characters.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.91,1:15:06.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.68,1:15:07.95,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Icchan.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.98,1:15:11.89,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I went to the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.89,1:15:14.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her sisters beloved gâteau au chocolat.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.79,1:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.46,1:15:20.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.23,1:15:23.40,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.80,1:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.46,1:15:24.03,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.13,1:15:26.37,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.37,1:15:28.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.60,1:15:34.91,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,359,\alpha0)} I almost cried but I bought soba by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.11,1:15:38.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her big sister loves soba.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.51,1:15:40.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone is sharing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.58,1:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmh.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.95,1:15:48.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the meal they play cards for the first time in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.56,1:15:55.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Karin, please don't get too hotheaded again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.56,1:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All around well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.64,1:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,An errand for an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.64,1:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And she did apologize, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.67,1:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.47,1:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.78,1:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It hit bull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.11,1:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.65,1:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy she was able to say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.01,1:16:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,885)}I was worried that the 2 yen didn't amount to anything but she did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.05,1:16:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Smashing the piggy bank and only finding 2 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.42,1:16:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what can you do with 2 yen?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.99,1:16:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotta, you also cried a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.39,1:16:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.39,1:16:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A siblings fight. Yeah, it's not good.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.39,1:16:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A siblings fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.03,1:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it remind you of your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.36,1:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right when we fought...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.16,1:16:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never apologize sincerely.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.20,1:16:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What an honest child.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.27,1:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- but the whole town felt so warm. What a nice upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.71,1:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.64,1:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it makes you want to be raised in such a town.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.31,1:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I live in Tokyo it's just not like that here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.25,1:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But there it seems like everyone knows each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.75,1:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from an "Errand" fan. Great analysis.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.29,1:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.29,1:17:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is the big adventure of a talkative little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.58,1:17:04.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When bringing up the subject of an errand
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.57,1:17:07.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she became so delighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.17,1:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, can you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.34,1:17:11.04,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yaaay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.04,1:17:13.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(65.25,507)}Hikari {\fs30}\N 3 years\N 4 months
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.04,1:17:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.01,1:17:17.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her fathers handmade flag for crossing the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.76,1:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(851.625,563)}I'm crossing. \N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.34,1:17:22.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will be highly visible since it reflects the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.44,1:17:22.97,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(120.375,355)}Hikari {\fs30}\N 3 years\N 4 months
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.42,1:17:24.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,3 years and 4 months?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.75,1:17:26.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Full of vigor and hates losing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.18,1:17:26.99,GreenFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,492,\alpha0)\pos(317.25,841)}Big brother
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.18,1:17:26.99,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,492,\alpha0)\pos(420.75,419)}Father
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.18,1:17:26.99,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,492,\alpha0)\pos(797.625,573)}Mother
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.05,1:17:30.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She smooth talks her, 2-year older, brother to get him to do things.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.52,1:17:35.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone says she was born with a gift of chatter.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.66,1:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(102.375,213)}Saitama ● Chichibu
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.66,1:17:37.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Talking about errands
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.20,1:17:40.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,there's not a single shop closeby.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.73,1:17:47.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, there is a single shop. A mechanic. So her mother is sending her on an errand to get a car fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.08,1:17:50.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It has a light scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.51,1:17:54.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's an errand to get a forgotten object inside of the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.11,1:17:55.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the forgotten thing is...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.82,1:17:59.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A pink photo album that Hikari knows well.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.62,1:18:00.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Inside it...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.25,1:18:05.06,OrangeFill,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF\t(0,526,\alpha0)\pos(688.5,296)}Mother
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.39,1:18:05.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When her mother was young and on a young people cultural exchange program.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.53,1:18:08.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She helped as a midwife.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.73,1:18:10.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,Full of experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.63,1:18:14.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The friends from 15 years ago came to their house yesterday and they held a party.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.80,1:18:20.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the friends feigned having forgotten the photo album in the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.97,1:18:25.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To get to the mechanic she has to follow the long road
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.78,1:18:31.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and she was asked to get two peach juice bottles from the vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.42,1:18:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The dazzling smile of
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.95,1:18:34.15,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Hikarichan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.15,1:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The dazzling smile of
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.59,1:18:36.82,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Hikarichan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.69,1:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.56,1:18:40.06,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.06,1:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.03,1:18:45.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Full of vigor and hates losing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.00,1:18:46.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Off she goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.04,1:18:52.57,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\t(1852,1852,\fs110)}How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.14,1:18:53.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\t(1852,1852,\fs110)}How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.57,1:18:54.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\t(1852,1852,\fs110)}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.34,1:18:59.21,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,How did they forget it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.31,1:18:59.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.21,1:19:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's complaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.01,1:19:02.48,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.48,1:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She said good grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.48,1:19:06.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she will go get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.66,1:19:13.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Recently she's been learning her numbers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.96,1:19:14.39,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.84,1:19:25.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can even count past 21?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.91,1:19:26.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.57,1:19:29.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can count to 39.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.44,1:19:30.91,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm so smart!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.21,1:19:38.49,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, {\alphaFF\t(892,892,\alpha0)}it's within sight. {\alphaFF\t(2994,2994,\alpha0)}It's within sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.49,1:19:39.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.69,1:19:43.96,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If I go there the photo album should be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.96,1:19:45.93,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm so smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.26,1:19:48.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has spotted the mint green wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.30,1:19:51.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her eyes are as sharp as her mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.27,1:19:56.54,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Here I don't have to be too attentive to cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.54,1:19:59.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She even knows the term for "being attentive to cars".
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.54,1:20:01.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right, there are no crossings here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.64,1:20:04.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's straight ahead on this one road.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.01,1:20:05.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's so smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.15,1:20:09.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The weather is nice and not windy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.48,1:20:10.55,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.55,1:20:11.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.85,1:20:13.65,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The wind is blowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.65,1:20:16.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what her mother always exclaims when she's hanging clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.72,1:20:17.96,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\alpha0\t(492,0,\alphaFF)}Phew.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.96,1:20:18.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.99,1:20:21.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has learned to say good grief from her brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.86,1:20:23.53,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.53,1:20:25.17,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Looks like it will rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.37,1:20:27.17,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Looks like it will rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.17,1:20:29.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's also what her mother often says.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.00,1:20:32.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not a chance that it will rain today.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.46,1:20:59.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has finally arrived at the crossing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.40,1:21:02.87,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Should I be attentive to cars?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.87,1:21:04.71,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,[Baby talk.]
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.91,1:21:07.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since there's no crossing around here
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.41,1:21:10.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the father has talked with the traffic police
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.51,1:21:13.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who has lent him a safety cone.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.88,1:21:16.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dazzling smile of Hikarichan.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.02,1:21:18.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will she notice it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.52,1:21:22.56,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.56,1:21:24.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Beep.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.40,1:21:32.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father, {\alphaFF\t(1485,1485,\alpha0)}Hikari is doing it properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.40,1:21:34.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.27,1:21:38.27,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,There are none. {\alphaFF\t(2121,2121,\alpha0)}I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.27,1:21:42.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her hands are free cause she doesn't have to carry the flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.94,1:21:47.28,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's within sight. {\alphaFF\t(2126,2126,\alpha0)}I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.51,1:21:49.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,How great that I made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.99,1:21:55.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The white car belongs to her household.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.29,1:21:58.39,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,The vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.39,1:22:00.76,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,If I go there, will I arrive?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.09,1:22:04.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's getting the peach juice first.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.63,1:22:06.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.47,1:22:08.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The silver ones are 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.07,1:22:10.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the brown are 10 yen. She knows that well.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.60,1:22:13.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The peach juice costs 110 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.91,1:22:15.78,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,How high.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.91,1:22:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(547.875,49)}The word for expensive and tall is the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.24,1:22:18.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not the price but the button.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.61,1:22:23.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother asked her to get the juice on the top row so that she has to call the old man for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.78,1:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.52,1:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.72,1:22:30.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can reach the money slot but...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.86,1:22:32.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,How will she do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.43,1:22:36.60,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Though it's so close to me {\alphaFF\t(2419,2419,\alpha0)}I just can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.60,1:22:39.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The peach juice that's close but far.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.67,1:22:42.20,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can't reach up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.20,1:22:44.47,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Can't reach even if I jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.81,1:22:47.31,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,919)}{\alpha0\t(1818,0,\alphaFF)}Ah, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.17,1:22:48.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though she could go and ask the mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.91,1:22:54.85,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can't reach {\alphaFF\t(1457,1457,\alpha0)}up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.85,1:22:58.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's been mumbling to herself for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.65,1:23:02.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's so high up there. How difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.76,1:23:05.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.53,1:23:08.80,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.23,1:23:09.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing. She can yell.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.80,1:23:11.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She called out with a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.70,1:23:16.37,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.50,1:23:18.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh, over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.07,1:23:21.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's rare that a small customer stops by.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.24,1:23:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.01,1:23:23.08,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.08,1:23:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.88,1:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will carry you so you can push.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.02,1:23:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.35,1:23:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.19,1:23:34.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's letting her do it herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.39,1:23:37.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.59,1:23:40.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After 20 minutes she finally got one bottle.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.49,1:23:44.80,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And... {\alphaFF\t(2027,2027,\alpha0)}Mama said to buy two.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.80,1:23:47.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mama told Hikari, "I'll leave it up to you."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.87,1:23:49.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was asked by her mother but...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.67,1:23:52.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old man is wondering if it's only about juice.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.31,1:23:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you only come to buy juice?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.94,1:23:58.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.98,1:24:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.38,1:24:01.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about the photo album?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.42,1:24:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.62,1:24:04.68,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.68,1:24:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.62,1:24:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else that you need to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.12,1:24:07.52,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.52,1:24:10.09,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I didn't forget a single thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.09,1:24:14.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh, she remembered. Yeah. That thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.86,1:24:16.40,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.83,1:24:20.03,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.03,1:24:23.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When she purchased the second one she put in 200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.27,1:24:27.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She remembered about the change. 90 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.37,1:24:29.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She forgot the change.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.37,1:24:31.18,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.18,1:24:32.91,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,It's good that I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.68,1:24:34.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,How good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.85,1:24:39.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has completely forgotten about the thing in the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.75,1:24:43.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As she's about to head home the phone rings at the mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.32,1:24:49.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the mother. It's been an hour since she left home and she's worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.50,1:24:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.63,1:24:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hikari come that way?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.83,1:24:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I talk with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.14,1:24:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.61,1:25:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A phone call from mama. Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.74,1:25:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.28,1:25:03.44,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.44,1:25:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.11,1:25:09.98,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,I got two peach juice out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.98,1:25:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to buy the peach juice?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.72,1:25:14.92,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,And with that {\alphaFF\t(1322,1322,\alpha0)}I will come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.92,1:25:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.99,1:25:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nonchan
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.76,1:25:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,said that she forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.33,1:25:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The photo album. {\alphaFF\t(2186,2186,\alpha0)}The pink one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.46,1:25:22.70,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,919)}Yep yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.73,1:25:25.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,She remembered.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.50,1:25:26.03,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.03,1:25:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.63,1:25:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.63,1:25:29.30,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.07,1:25:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What did your mother tell you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.41,1:25:35.11,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Album.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.87,1:25:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Album?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.24,1:25:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.44,1:25:37.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.78,1:25:39.35,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.58,1:25:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.35,1:25:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's look for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.08,1:25:43.45,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.45,1:25:46.99,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Yay, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.32,1:25:46.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pink album.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.99,1:25:51.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The thing that she wondered "how her mother's friends forgot".
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.73,1:25:52.73,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.73,1:25:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.73,1:25:56.36,WhitePurpleBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.36,1:25:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.03,1:26:00.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How did they forget it?
