Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.98,1:34:30.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also how to pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.58,1:34:33.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the names of various products.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.48,1:34:36.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright and today it's collagen. right?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.28,1:34:39.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Chicken thighs, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.32,1:34:41.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,Chicken thighs.
